1. WHAT WE BUILT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

A unified multi-target compilation pipeline for Fe:

  Fe source code
      ↓ compile_to_ir(db, top_mod, target)
  Sonatina IR (shared, target-agnostic)
      ↓                    ↓                    ↓
  CraneliftBackend    WasmBackend         SpirvBackend
  (JIT execution)     (via WAFFLE)        (via Naga)
      ↓                    ↓                    ↓
  Native code         .wasm module        SPIR-V shader
  (executes)          (wasmtime)          (spirv-val ✓)

Proven with parameterized functions:
  pub fn compute(a: u64, b: u64) -> u64 { a + b + a * b + 42 }
  → Cranelift: 85 ✓  WASM: 85 ✓  SPIR-V: validated ✓

