40+ Sonatina IR instructions handled:
  Arithmetic: Add, Sub, Mul, Neg, Udiv, Sdiv, Shl, Shr, Sar
  Logic: And, Or, Xor, Not
  Compare: Lt, Gt, Le, Ge, Slt, Sgt, Sle, Sge, Eq, Ne, IsZero
  Cast: Sext, Zext, Trunc
  Control: Jump, Br, Return, Call (sret + intrinsic), Unreachable
